nh 4 life.

item.title: How to edit ip on a client?
item.dc:creator: @lamename5 lamename5
item.description:
@lamename5 wrote:

Is it an open or closed scource? If it is a
closed scource (meaning it doesn’t have .java files, and
only .class files) you will have to decompile it.
Just google “Cavaj Java Decompiler”
and download it, and use common sense.
